data.title: Dylan O'Brien: Credits, Bio, News & More
data.meta_description: Searching to find out more about Dylan O'Brien? We have a full Biography, Photos, Theatre Credits, TV and Movies, Videos and more! Check out Dylan O'Brien's bio now including film and tv, as well as on stage.
data.text:
Dylan O'Brien News

Video: Heléne Yorke, Josh Segarra & More Star in THE OTHER TWO Season Three Trailer

Watch the new video trailer for the third season of The Other Two, which features Broadway alums Heléne Yorke, Josh Segarra, and Molly Shannon. As previously reported, the new season will also feature Ben Platt, Edie Falco, Richard Kind, and Kate Berlant.

Taylor Swift's 'All Too Well' Beats 'American Pie' as Longest #1 Hit of All Time

Don McLean’s “American Pie,” has been replaced by Taylor Swift’s “All Too Well,” as the longest #1 hit of all time. McLean will appear on The Colbert Show tonight to talk about the 50th Anniversary of the song. Watch Taylor Swift's 'All Too Well' short film starring Sadie Sink and Dylan O'Brien now!

Taylor Swift Debuts 'Red (Taylor's Version)'

Taylor Swift has released the re-recorded version of her hit album 'Red'. The 30-track album features collaborations with Ed Sheeran, Phoebe Bridgers, Chris Stapleton, and more. The 'All Too Well' short film will debut tonight, starring Sadie Sink and Dylan O'Brien. Listen to the new album now!

Mark Rylance, Johnny Flynn & More Will Star in Graham Moore's THE OUTFIT

Tony and Academy Award winner Mark Rylance (The Trial of the Chicago 7), Dylan O’Brien (The Maze Runner series), Zoey Deutch (Set It Up) and Johnny Flynn (EMMA.) are set to star. Producers are Scoop Wasserstein, Ben Browning and Amy Jackson.

'MTV Reunions' Kicks Off With TEEN WOLF This June

MTV today announced its new digital format, 'MTV Reunions,' will launch with the cast and creator of the iconic series 'Teen Wolf' on Friday, June 5th at 12PM ET/PT for its 9th anniversary.

VIDEO: Watch the Trailer for Steven Spielberg's AMAZING STORIES Reboot

Five tales. Infinite imagination. Watch Amazing Stories on March 6 on the Apple TV app with an Apple TV+ subscription.

Apple Announces Premiere Date for Steven Spielberg's AMAZING STORIES

Apple TV+'s highly anticipated original series, executive produced by visionary, award-winning filmmaker Steven Spielberg, will make its global debut on Friday, March 6, exclusively on Apple TV+. The premiere date and a first look image from the series were revealed at the Television Critics Association Winter Press Tour.

Apple TV+ Announces Premiere Dates For Upcoming Series; Spielbergs 'Amazing Stories,' 'Home,' and More!

Apple TV Plus has announced premiere dates for a slew of its upcoming series, according to Variety.

Mark Wahlberg's INFINITE Adds Chiwetel Ejiofor

Variety reports that actor Chiwetel Ejiofor will star in action thriller 'Infinite' alongside Mark Wahlberg. Antoine Fuqua directs, and Paramount will produce.

Dylan O'Brien Will Star in INFINITE Opposite Mark Wahlberg

Variety reports that Dylan O'Brien will star in the action thriller 'Infinite.' Mark Wahlberg and Sophie Cookson have also been announced as members of the cast. Antoine Fuqua directs.

YouTube Announces Fall 2018 Slate and 2019 Projects

YouTube Announces Fall 2018 Slate and 2019 Projects

YouTube Announces Fall 2018 Slate and 2019 Projects

Today at the Television Critics Association session, YouTube showcased its upcoming Original series and announced renewals for 2018/2019. From ambitious projects and compelling documentaries showcasing YouTube stars, to inventive comedies, bold dramas and live events featuring from some of the biggest names in Hollywood, YouTube continues to offer innovative programming that engages its audience. Since the launch of YouTube Originals in 2015, Original content has been viewed more than 650 million times.

Dylan O'Brien & Maika Monroe Join Cast of THE EDUCATION OF FREDRICK FITZELL

According to The Hollywood Reporter, Dylan O'Brien and Maika Monroe are set to lead the cast of THE EDUCATION OF FREDRICK FITZELL. The film was written by Christopher MacBride, who is also set to direct. MINDHUNTER star Hannah Gross has also been cast. Read more about the news from The Hollywood Reporter here!

Review Roundup: Do Critics Think AMERICAN ASSASSIN is Killer?

AMERICAN ASSASSIN follows the rise of Mitch Rapp (Dylan O'Brien), a CIA Black Ops recruit under the instruction of Cold War veteran Stan Hurley (Michael Keaton). The pair is then enlisted by CIA Deputy Director Irene Kennedy (Sanaa Lathan) to investigate a wave of apparently random attacks on both military and civilian targets.

BWW Picks the Best and Worst Character Arcs on Television

Today, we've assembled our picks for the best and worst character arcs on television, featuring characters that have grown immensely on their respected shows and others who have greatly deteriorated over time.

BEAUTY & THE BEAST, Harry Styles Among Winners of TEEN CHOICE 2017; Full List

The following were honored today at TEEN CHOICE 2017, which aired live on FOX from the University of Southern California's Galen Center in Los Angeles. This year, teens logged on to Twitter and FOX.com and cast more than 63 million votes in support of their favorite teen icons in film, television, music, sports, fashion, comedy and the web.

Justin Bieber Among Final Wave of TEEN CHOICE 2017 Nominees; Full List

TEEN CHOICE 2017TM, the summer's hottest LIVE show, has announced the second and final wave of nominees. Selena Gomez leads Wave Two nominations with eight nominations across music and social media categories, while Justin Bieber follows with seven.

WONDER WOMAN, PRETTY LITTLE LIARS Among First Wave of TEEN CHOICE 2017 Nominees

TEEN CHOICE 2017TM, the summer's hottest LIVE show is back with a brand-new wave of nominees. Leading the television category with seven nods is “Pretty Little Liars,” followed by “The Flash,” with four.

Lionsgate Expands Output Deal with Central Partnership in Russia

Lionsgate a premier next generation global content leader, has strengthened its presence in a key international territory by entering a new output agreement with Russian distributor Central Partnership for the distribution of Lionsgate and Summit Entertainment films in Russia and the Commonwealth of Independent States
